{"tid":1751970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊抗爭方向","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:40:59.000Z","uid":245713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66d85bb5b303421adbe3b140c82865246c3b7420","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:07.000Z","msg":"如果今次贏到，我地一黎要謝票，要多謝全香港人<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得我哋個方向可以用<br />\n重建香港，釋放所有學生<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n爭取所有抗爭者以社會服務令取代坐監，大家修復番之前破壞既無辜地方(黃色經濟圈就當然要keep)<br />\n俾個好啲既下檯階政府同民建聯<br />\n<br />\n繼續追求五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n政府一定要拎番啲誠意，應承幾個先，以灰復社會運作，剩底既再坐低大家傾，唔係傾做唔做，係傾點做！<br />\n<br />\n民陣開始番每星期大遊行，直至五大訴求番黎！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"08b52781b65f046b275a0c9f9f21f00a75ab9e70","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7af3e8d8987137bc09eaac42326d72e17315a7a","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:38.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c09f88bfb8281268d896dae6322187c9f6ca8648","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"同意，唔同意都好，覆一覆我"},{"pid":"ac3e98525f37ba9e2926c08f91dee5c73678fcb0","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:36:22.000Z","msg":"今次贏咗既議員係時候出力啦"},{"pid":"d3b9aecf96204afbc2f23d5a36ec90ba0df247cf","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:36:45.000Z","msg":"唔好再好似以前啲議員咁，乜都唔做"},{"pid":"e185d3a854982a20b936a61a237b3f5c7096cbf0","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:37:02.000Z","msg":"所有被自殺都要徹查"},{"pid":"47cf062cca63ecaac7bcebb9913b8d75a66b242e","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e185d3a854982a20b936a61a237b3f5c7096cbf0","tid":1751970,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20